Full Description: 3-month entrepreneurship accelerator for Foreign Nationals to conduct permissible activities while in the USA on a WB/WT visa waiver. No business plan or concept is required.  The Exempt Venture Capital Investment Fund Adviser collectively identifies and performs due diligence on start-up companies led by foreign nationals. Independent researchers are invited on a B-1 Business Visitor Visa for 6-months to a year. Nonimmigrants must be eligible for WB, B-1, F-1 OPT or J-1 (without 2-year restriction).  The Visa Waiver Program (VWP) operated by the U.S. Department of State enables nationals of certain countries to travel to the United States of America for business (WB) for stays of 90 days or less without obtaining a visa.  VWP eligible travelers may apply for a B-1 Business Visitor visa, if they want to participate in the incubator track (6 months to 1 year). Not all countries participate in the VWP, and not all travelers from VWP countries are eligible to use the program. F-1 OPT international students can maintain status in the USA with proper authorization as defined by Department of Homeland Security Policy Guidance 1004-03 — Update to Optional Practical Training, Paragraph 7.2 Employment allowed while on OPT. J-1 Exchange Visitors (without a 2-year restriction) and F-1 OPT candidates can participate to possibly qualify for H-1B status. A Self-Enrichment Educator assists foreign nationals to develop a "trade secret," any formula, pattern, device or compilation of information which is used in their business, and which gives them an opportunity to obtain an advantage over competitors who do not know or use it.

Description: PX Interactive are developers of the NetDog networking engine for MMOs and Virtual Worlds. Netdog is positioned as a high performance
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: PX Interactive are developers of the NetDog networking engine for MMOs and Virtual Worlds.  Netdog is positioned as a high performance toolset for game developers and virtual world designers.  As such, primary features include load balancing and load distribution tools, seamless world functionality, performance optimization tools, and an intuitive interface that is easy to learn and customize. NetDog has two major features.  First, NetDog is fully cross-platform - developers will be able to create games that can be played across PC, Mac, PS3, Xbox 360, and even iPhone.  Network messages will work regardless of the platform, bringing more gamers into each game, and providing unique gameplay options.   Second, NetDog's architecture is built on a patent-pending distributed networking solution.  With small setting changes NetDog can be used in a variety of network topologies - from full client server mode to fully peer-to-peer, with a variety of network computing options in-between.  Developers will have the option to off-load some or all of their game processing to the clients in their network, and can choose which functions and events will be handled where.  This will allow for bigger, more efficient networks with lower latencies PX Interactive overview PX Interactive is led by a team of technologists and game industry veterans with entrepreneurial experience.  The company's objective is to become the top player in the defined niche of high-speed networking for 3D worlds.  As such, they are targetting game developers and virtual world designers of all sizes.

A Will saves your spouse and children money and hassle, and ensures your wishes are carried out. Their service allows people who live in North America to create their own legally compliant Wills online for a small fee. It takes less than a half hour to do, and the result is a Will that will stand up in court in all 50 states. Once your Will is created and signed, you can rest assured that your estate will be handled the way you want and at minimal expense to your spouse and children. They created this service because they think that everyone should be able to create a legally binding Will in the privacy of their own home. If you take the future of your loved ones seriously and want to make sure that you retain control of your hard-earned assets, let them help you create a legally compliant last Will and testament today.
